{"tid":2055370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聖公會主風小學稱不足10名學生住祿泉樓 檢測呈陰性","createTime":"2020-06-08T02:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T04:43:13.000Z","uid":166360,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"daf7b99a3558aab011bc47f2e8d32a91f500ddc2","tid":2055370,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"聖公會主風小學稱不足10名學生住祿泉樓 檢測呈陰性<br />\n2020-06-08 HKT 09:46<br />\n<br />\n小四至中二學生今日復課。早前有多人確診的沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓，附近多間中小學維持復課安排。其中在聖公會主風小學，副校長田少斌表示，學校有不足10名學生居住在祿泉樓，全部人都已經完成檢測，結果呈陰性。他又表示，如果有家長仍然擔心，可以選擇為子女請假，校方不會當學生曠課。<br />\n<br />\n有祿泉樓附近小學的家長表示，不容許子女帶零食回校，認為在校內進食不太安全，又指學校鄰近祿泉樓，會感到擔心，但小朋友喜愛返學，所以不會考慮請假。她會提醒小朋友勤洗手、在校內不要除下口罩等。<br />\n<br />\n有中學生表示，由於擔心疫情，所以在5月底開學時，曾請假數日，認為現時只要做足防疫措施便不會有事。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530767-20200608.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530767-20200608.htm&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=14269950\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530767-20200608.htm&h=ddf80425\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530767-20200608.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撐復課</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0266e418e066b3d40696538056e465f8cc8729d9","tid":2055370,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />防疫？不了<br />\n要抗疫！"},{"pid":"999f96c8f1e14f558a8fd8bb4d374f31dee71be6","tid":2055370,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:09:07.000Z","msg":"留番幾個樣本過多十日之後攞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b867a90ce27601aaeb5bc6aa2e6f28e2abc0177","tid":2055370,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:10:11.000Z","msg":"到續限聚令咪有陽性囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5171a86a640967536dacc5bbcfea49fc34aad3da","tid":2055370,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"但小朋友喜愛返學，所以不會考慮請假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e0e7c036f295f0d7a09b7bef0ef585a888d9b9","tid":2055370,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5171a86a640967536dacc5bbcfea49fc34aad3da","tid":2055370,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"但小朋友喜愛返學，所以不會考慮請假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"小學的家長表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}